{"tid":726020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[吓？] 最安全旅遊地 日本印度竟同級","createTime":"2018-07-02T05:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T07:26:03.000Z","uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4f86c9d83b3d1e1ebc688f7a7f46117a5e220cf4","tid":726020,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"【訪當地民眾列最安全旅遊地】 <br />\n【日本、印度並列 25 名】<br />\n<br />\nCNN 根一據 2018 年蓋洛普全球法律及秩序報告(Gallup survey)，列出全球最安全旅遊地方名單。<br />\n<br />\n蓋洛普去年在 142 個國家及地區，訪問近 15 萬名，15 歲以上的民眾，包括對警方的信任程度、晚上獨自外出安全感、及過去一年曾否遇劫等罪案經歷，列出分數後得出排名。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡獲選為全球最安全旅遊地方，北歐國家挪威、冰島及芬蘭排第二。<br />\n<br />\n香港排名第五，顯示受訪者對治安有一定信心。<br />\n<br />\n但值得留意的是，較冷門位於中亞的烏茲別克，亦並列第五。<br />\n<br />\n調查員估計如烏茲別克般極權政府統治下的地方，民眾可能曾被搶劫或襲擊，但不敢在受訪時說真話。<br />\n<br />\n數據未必反映真實治安情況，排名僅供參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港人旅遊熱點的日本，只能與印度、緬甸、德國等並列 25 名。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#CNN　#印度　#日本　#旅遊國家　#新加坡　#香港　#icablenews　#hknews　#cablenews　#newsdaily　#news<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/877012649157471/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F877012649157471%2F&d=uLK1R3VyKD4%2BN24X34HBUm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5fc81706\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/877012649157471/</a>"},{"pid":"123a04cea4a17218b253153de69a12f7cf96f0b7","tid":726020,"uid":36857,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"CNN<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9b796d1bb3aae42deb8191c99872c92bacb745","tid":726020,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f370f850e1d1aea7f39f2b95a8fbc2adff518693","tid":726020,"uid":35468,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"CNN真